quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Pali iwo amene amasonkhana kukhala pa maudindo osiyanasiyana
  37,2,Pali iwo amene amayendetsa mitambo mwa ubwino
  37,3,Pali iwo amene amabweretsa m’Buku ndi Korani kuchokera kwa Mulungu kupita nalo kwa anthu ake
  37,4,Ndithudi Mulungu wanu ndi mmodzi yekha
  37,5,Ambuye wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi wa zonse zimene zili m’menemo ndi Ambuye wa dera lililonse lotulukira dzuwa
  37,6,Ndithudi Ife tidakongoletsa mtambo woyandikira kwambiri ndi nyenyezi
  37,7,Ndi kulonda Satana wofukira
  37,8,Kotero iwo sangathe kumvetsera zokambidwa za gulu lapamwamba chifukwa iwo amapirikitsidwa kuchokera kumbali iliyonse
  37,9,"Atapirikitsidwa, chawo chidzakhala chilango chosatha"
  37,10,"Kupatula yekhayo amene amakwatula zinthu mwakuba, ndipo amathamangitsidwa ndi moto woyaka ndi wowala kwambiri"
  37,11,"Ndipo tawafunsa, “Kodi iwo ndi a mphamvu kuposa zolengedwa zina zimene tidalenga?” Iwo tidawalenga kuchokera ku dothi lonyata la makande"
  37,12,"Iyayi, iwe udadabwa pamene iwo anali kunyoza"
  37,13,"Ndipo iwo akamaweruzidwa, iwo safuna kuweruzidwa"
  37,14,Ndipo iwo akaona chizindikiro chochokera kwa Mulungu amachisandutsa ngati chinthu choseweretsa
  37,15,"Ndipo amati, “Ichi si china ayi koma matsenga woonekera poyera.”"
  37,16,"“Chiyani! Ife tikafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, kodi tidzaukitsidwa?”"
  37,17,“Ndiponso makolo athu amakedzana?”
  37,18,"Nena, “Inde mudzachititsidwa manyazi.”"
  37,19,Ndipo udzakhala mfuwu umodzi ndipo taona iwo adzakhala ali kupenyetsetsana
  37,20,"Iwo adzati, “Tsoka kwa ife! Ili ndi tsiku lachiweruzo.”"
  37,21,“Ili ndi tsiku lachiweruzo limene inu mumati ndi bodza.”
  37,22,(Kudzanenedwa kuti); “Bweretsani anthu ochimwa pamodzi ndi anzawo ndi zinthu zimene iwo anali kupembedza.”
  37,23,“Kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni ndipo atsogolereni ku njira ya kumoto.”
  37,24,"“Ndipo aimitseni. Ndithudi, iwo ayenera kufunsidwa.”"
  37,25,“Kodi mwatani? Nanga ndi chifukwa chiyani inu simuli kuthandizana?”
  37,26,Iyayi! Koma iwo lero ndi odzipereka
  37,27,Ndipo iwo adzafunsana wina ndi mnzake
  37,28,"Iwo adzati, “Ndinu amene munali kubwera kwa ife kuchokera kudzanja lamanja.”"
  37,29,"Iwo adzayankha kuti, “Iyayi, Inuyo simunali okhulupirira.”"
  37,30,“Ndipo ife tidalibe ulamuliro pa inu. Iyayi! Inu mudali osamva.”
  37,31,“Kotero chiweruzo cha Ambuye wathu chadza pa ife. Ndithudi tsopano tidzachilawa.”
  37,32,“Choncho ife tidakusocheretsani chifukwa nafenso tidali osochera.”
  37,33,"Ndipo, ndithudi, patsiku limeneli onse adzalandirana chilango pakati pa wina ndi mnzake"
  37,34,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timachitira ndi anthu olakwa
  37,35,"Ndithudi pamene iwo, adauzidwa kuti, “Kulibe mulungu wina koma Mulungu weniweni, iwo anali kudzitukumula.”"
  37,36,"Ndipo adanena kuti, “Kodi ife tisiye milungu yathu chifukwa cha Mlakatuli wamisala?”"
  37,37,Iyayi. Iye wadza ndi choonadi ndipo ali kutsimikizira uthenga wa Atumwi amene adadza kale
  37,38,"Ndithudi, inu mudzalangidwa kwambiri"
  37,39,Ndipo inu mudzalandira mphotho molingana ndi ntchito zanu
  37,40,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu
  37,41,Kwa iwo mphotho yawo ndi yodziwika
  37,42,Zipatso ndipo iwo adzalemekezeka kwambiri
  37,43,M’minda ya chisangalalo
  37,44,Atakhala pa mipando ya chifumu moyang’anizana
  37,45,Pakati pawo padzaperekedwa chikho cha vinyo wabwino
  37,46,oyera ndiponso okoma kwa iwo amene amamwa
  37,47,Simudzakhala mavuto mu icho ndipo sichidzawatopetsa
  37,48,Ndipo pakati pawo padzakhala akazi angwiro opanda chimasomaso
  37,49,Okhala ngati mazira osamalidwa bwino
  37,50,Ndipo adzadza kwa anzawo ndi kumafunsana wina ndi mnzake
  37,51,"Wina wochokera pakati pawo adzayankhula nati, “Ndithudi ine ndinali ndi bwenzi langa.”"
  37,52,“Amene amakonda kunena kuti; “Kodi ndiwe mmodzi mwa okhulupirira?”
  37,53,"“Kodi ife tikafa ndi kusanduka dothi ndi mafupa, tidzatengedwa kupita ku chiweruzo"
  37,54,"Iye adati, “Kodi iwe ungaone pansi?”"
  37,55,Motero adayang’ana pansi ndipo adamuona iye ali pakati pa moto wa ku Gahena
  37,56,"Iye adati, “Pali Mulungu! Iwe udatsala pang’ono kundipweteka.”"
  37,57,"“Ndipo kukadapanda chisomo cha Ambuye wanga ine, ndithudi, ndikadakhala mmodzi wa iwo.”"
  37,58,“Kodi ndiye kuti ife sitidzafa?”
  37,59,"“Kupatula kufa koyamba, kodi ife sitidzalangidwa?”"
  37,60,Ndithudi uku ndiko kupambana kwenikweni
  37,61,"Pofuna kupeza zotere, alekereni alimbikire amene akufuna kuti alimbikirewo"
  37,62,Kodi chimenechi ndi chabwino kapena mtengo wa Zaqqum
  37,63,Ndithudi tazipanga izi kukhala mayesero kwa anthu olakwa
  37,64,Ndithudi umenewu ndi mtengo umene umamera pansi pa Gahena
  37,65,Zipatso zake zili ngati mitu ya a Satana
  37,66,Ndithudi iwo adzadya zimenezi ndi kukhutitsa mimba zawo ndi zipatsozo
  37,67,"Ndithudi iwo akadzadya, adzamwa chakumwa chokonzedwa ndi madzi owira"
  37,68,Ndithudi iwo adzapita ku Gahena
  37,69,Ndithudi iwo adapeza makolo awo ali osochera
  37,70,Kotero iwo ali kutsatira mapazi awo
  37,71,Ndithudi makolo awo adasochera iwo asanadze
  37,72,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ife tidatumiza Atumwi pakati pawo"
  37,73,Ndipo taona zimene zidadza kwa iwo amene adachenjezedwa
  37,74,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu omwe ndi anthu olungama
  37,75,Ndipo ndithudi Nowa adatipempha Ife ndipo Ife timayankha bwino pa amene amayankha
  37,76,Ndipo Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi banja lake ku chilango choopsa
  37,77,Ndipo tidapulumutsanso ana ake
  37,78,Ndipo tidakhazikitsa ulemu pa iye pakati pa mitundu yonse yamtsogolo
  37,79,Mtendere ukhale kwa Nowa kuchokera kwa zolengedwa zonse
  37,80,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timalipirira anthu ochita zabwino
  37,81,Ndithudi iye adali mmodzi mwa akapolo athu okhulupirira
  37,82,Ndipo ena onse tidawamiza
  37,83,Ndithudi pakati pa iwo amene amatsatira njira yake adali Abrahamu
  37,84,Pamene iye adadza kwa Ambuye wake ndi mtima woyera
  37,85,"Pamene iye adati kwa atate wake ndi anthu a mtundu wake, “Kodi ndi chiyani chimene inu muli kupembedza?”"
  37,86,“Kodi mukufuna milungu yabodza kapena Mulungu weniweni?”
  37,87,“Kodi mukuganiza zotani za Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse?”
  37,88,Ndipo iye adayang’ana nyenyezi
  37,89,"Ndipo iye adati, “Ndithudi ndili kudwala.”"
  37,90,Kotero iwo adamusiya ndi kubwerera
  37,91,"Ndipoiyeadayang’anakwamilunguyawonati, “Kodi inu simudya?”"
  37,92,“Kodi bwanji inu simuyankhula?”
  37,93,Ndipo iye adadza pafupi ndi iyo ndi kuigwetsa ndi dzanja lake lamanja
  37,94,Nthawi yomweyo wopembedza mafano adadza kwa iye mwamsangamsanga
  37,95,"Iye adati, “Kodi mumapembedza zinthu zimene inu mwasema?”"
  37,96,“Pamene Mulungu ndiye amene adakulengani inu pamodzi ndi zosemasema zanuzi!”
  37,97,"Iwo adati, “Mupangireni ng’anjo ndipo muponyeni m’moto woyaka!”"
  37,98,Iwo adachita chiwembu koma Ife tidawachititsa manyazi
  37,99,"Ndipo iye adati, “Ine ndithawira kwa Ambuye wanga. Ndipo Iye adzanditsogolera ine.”"
  37,100,“Ambuye wanga! Ndipatseni ana kuchokera kwa ochita ntchito zabwino.”
  37,101,Ndipo Ife tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya mwana wamwamuna wopirira
  37,102,"Ndipo pamene iye adakula mofika pa msinkhu woti angathe kuthandiza abambo ake, iye adati: “Mwana wanga! Ndithudi ine ndalota ndili kukupha ngati nsembe. Taganiza zimene uli kuziona.” Iye adati, “Atate wanga! Inu chitani monga momwe mwalamulidwira. Ngati Mulungu afuna, mudzandipeza ine wopirira!”"
  37,103,"Ndipo pamene onse adadzipereka, ndipo adamugoneka iye chafufumimba"
  37,104,"Ndipo Ife tidamuitana ndipo tidati, “Iwe Abrahamu!”"
  37,105,“Ndithudi wakwaniritsa maloto ako.” Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita zabwino
  37,106,Ndithudi awa adali mayesero oonekeratu
  37,107,Ndipo tidamupatsa iye nsembe yaikulu
  37,108,Ndipo Ife tidakhazikitsa ulemu pa iye pakati pa mibadwo yamtsogolo
  37,109,Mtendere ukhale pa Abrahamu
  37,110,Mmenemo ndi mmene timalipira mphotho kwa anthu ochita zabwino
  37,111,Ndithudi iye adali mmodzi wa akapolo athu okhulupirira
  37,112,"Ndipo Ife tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya Isake, Mtumwi, wochokera pakati pa anthu okhulupirira"
  37,113,Ndipo Ife tidaika madalitso athu pa iye ndi pa Isake. Ndipo pakati pa ana awo pali ena ochita ntchito zabwino ndi ena amene ndi olakwa ndipo amadzipondereza okha
  37,114,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidaonetsa chisomo chathu kwa Mose ndi Aroni"
  37,115,Ndipo tidawapulumutsa onse pamodzi ndi anthu awo ku mavuto oopsa
  37,116,Ndipo Ife tidawathandiza kotero adali opambana
  37,117,Ndipo Ife tidawapatsa Buku Lopatulika limene limathandiza kufotokoza zinthu momveka bwino
  37,118,Ndipo Ife tidawatsogolera ku njira yoyenera
  37,119,Ndipo Ife tidakhazikitsa ulemu kwa iwo pakati pa mibadwo ya mtsogolo
  37,120,“Mtendere ukhale pa Mose ndi Aroni.”
  37,121,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita ntchito zabwino
  37,122,Ndithudi onse adali akapolo athu okhulupirira
  37,123,Ndithudi Eliya anali mmodzi wa Atumwi
  37,124,"Pamene, iye adati kwa anthu ake, “Kodi inu simungaope Mulungu?”"
  37,125,“Kodi muli kupembedza Bala ndi kusiya kupembedza Namalenga?”
  37,126,"“Mulungu, Ambuye wanu ndi Ambuye wa makolo anu akale?”"
  37,127,"Koma iwo adamukana iye ndipo ndithudi, iwo adzatengedwa"
  37,128,Kupatula akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu
  37,129,Ndithudi tidakhazikitsa ulemu kwa iye pakati pa mibadwo ya patsogolo
  37,130,“Mtendere ukhale ndi Eliya.”
  37,131,Ndithudi mmenemo ndi mmene timaperekera mphotho kwa anthu ochita ntchito zabwino
  37,132,Ndithudi iye adali mmodzi wa akopolo athu okhulupirira
  37,133,Ndipo Loti adali mmodzi wa Atumwi
  37,134,"Pamene, Ife tidamupulumutsa iye pamodzi ndi onse omutsatira"
  37,135,Kupatula mayi mmodzi wokalamba amene adali m’gulu la anthu otsalira m’mbuyo
  37,136,Ndipo Ife tidawaononga onse
  37,137,Ndithudi inu mumawadutsa nthawi ya m’mawa
  37,138,"Ndi nthawi yausiku, kodi inu simungazindikire"
  37,139,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Yona adali mmodzi wa Atumwi"
  37,140,Pamene iye adathawa kupita ku chombo chodzadza kwambiri ndi katundu
  37,141,Iye adachita nawo mayere koma iye adali mmodzi wa olephera
  37,142,Ndipo nsomba idamumeza iye chifukwa adalakwa
  37,143,Koma kukadakhala kuti sadapemphe chikhululukiro cha Mulungu wolemekezeka
  37,144,Ndithudi iye akadakhalabe m’mimba mwa nsomba mpaka tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa
  37,145,Koma Ife tidakamuponya pa mtunda pamene iye anali kudwala
  37,146,Ndipo Ife tidameretsa chitsamba cha chipanda kuti chimere pamwamba pake
  37,147,Ndipo tidamutumiza kwa anthu zikwi makumi khumi kapena kuposa apa
  37,148,Ndipo onse adakhulupirira ndipo Ife tidawapatsa chisangalalo cha kanthawi kochepa
  37,149,"Ndipo tsopano afunseni kuti, “Kodi Ambuye wako ali ndi ana"
  37,150,Kapena kuti Ife tidalenga angelo kukhala akazi pamene iwo anali kuona
  37,151,Kodi iwo sanena zabodza pamene amati
  37,152,“Mulungu wabereka mwana?” Ndithudi iwo ndi abodza
  37,153,Kodi iye adasankha ana aakazi m’malo mwa ana aamuna
  37,154,Kodi mwatani? Kodi mumaweruza bwanji
  37,155,Kodi simungaganize bwino
  37,156,Kapena kodi inu muli ndi ulamuliro weniweni
  37,157,Kotero bweretsani Buku lanu ngati ndinu olungama
  37,158,Ndipo iwo akhazikitsa ubale pakati pa Mulungu ndi majini. Koma majini amadziwa kuti iwo adzatengedwa kupita kwa Iye
  37,159,Ulemerero ukhale kwa Mulungu. Iye ali pamwamba pa zimene amamuyerekeza nazo
  37,160,"Kupatula akapolo a Mulungu, amene Iye amasankha"
  37,161,Ndithudi inu pamodzi ndi zimene mupembedza
  37,162,Simungathe kusocheza wina aliyense
  37,163,Kupatula okhawo amene adzapita ku moto wa ku Gahena
  37,164,Aliyense wa Ife ali ndi malo ake ake
  37,165,Ndithudi ndife amene timaima pa mizere kupemphera
  37,166,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ndife amene timamulemekeza"
  37,167,"Ndipo,\tndithudi,\tiwo\tanali\tkunena\tkuti"
  37,168,“Tikadakhala ndi chikumbutso monga chomwe chinali ndi anthu akale.”
  37,169,"“Ife, ndithudi, tidakhala akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu.”"
  37,170,Koma iwo sakhulupilira mu izi komabe iwo adzadziwa
  37,171,Ndithudi mawu athu adatsogola kwa akapolo athu omwe ndi Atumwi athu
  37,172,"Kuti iwo, ndithudi, adzathandizidwa"
  37,173,"Ndipo, ndithudi, gulu lathu lokha lidzakhala lopambana"
  37,174,Kotero uyambe wawasiya okha kwa kanthawi kochepa
  37,175,Ndipo uwaone ndipo iwo adzadzioneranso
  37,176,Kodi iwo afuna kufulumizitsa chilango chathu
  37,177,"Koma pamene icho chidzadza pa iwo, udzakhala m’mawa woipa kwa iwo amene adachenjezedwa"
  37,178,Kotero uyambe wawasiya okha kwa kanthawi kochepa
  37,179,Ndipo uwaone ndipo nawo adzaona
  37,180,"Ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wako, Ambuye wolemekezeka ndi wamphamvu, kuposa zimene ali kumukundikira"
  37,181,Ndipo mtendere ukhale kwa Atumwi onse
  37,182,"Ndipo kuyamikidwa ndi kuthokoza konse kukhale kwa Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse"